<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>You can create a busy indicator by replacing the &quot;indicator&quot; delegate of the <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls-styles-busyindicatorstyle.xml">BusyIndicatorStyle</db:link> with a custom design.</db:para>
<db:para>Example:</db:para>
<db:programlisting language="qml">BusyIndicator {
    style: BusyIndicatorStyle {
        indicator: Image {
            visible: control.running
            source: &quot;spinner.png&quot;
            RotationAnimator on rotation {
                running: control.running
                loops: Animation.Infinite
                duration: 2000
                from: 0 ; to: 360
            }
        }
    }
}
</db:programlisting>
</db:section>
